Pseudotime construction

In[]:
# Setting root cell as described above
root_ixs = adata.obsm["X_diffmap"][:, 3].argmin()
sc.pl.diffmap(
    adata,
    color=["cell_type"],
    components=['2, 3'],
)

adata.uns["iroot"] = root_ixs
